              I am, what I'm currently working on, and what I'm writing about at
              the moment.
              <br />
              <br />
              <span class="font-bold"
                >This is a cross-platform YouTube clone I built
              </span><span class="text-black">âœ¨</span><span class="font-bold"
                >:</span
              >
            </p>
            <div class="flex flex-row mx-auto">
              <Image
                src={homeImage}
                alt="Home Project"
                width={1370}
                height={802}
                loading="eager"
              />
            </div>
            <p class="text-center">
              Please feel free to view my React Native projects <a href="/projects">here</a>.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <Footer />
    </main>
  </body>
</html>
